  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even there the deception followed that if you're not well, you can go into hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the summer of '44, it was genuine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If you were not well, you could go into hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway, but nobody really wanted to because it was an extreme-- you didn't know-- they said it's warmer and you get a bit more food and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You don't have to go to appell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, there were certain benefits.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We knew people who came out of those hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we didn't know-- by the end of February, about 25, 26 of February, my father was getting a little bit weak.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, he could have still survived, because the liberation of Buchenwald was 11 of April.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we thought he can't so much to help himself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's better if he's in hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in he went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then thereafter, my brother and I left from that block-- I don't know how we got ourselves out, but there were too many ill people and whatnot-- and we went back down into block 67, which was in the zeltlager in the-- the-- in the canvas blocks.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So eventually, two, three weeks later, we were talking, and my brother and I, said, look, why not go into the hospital as well?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are together with our father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't forget, we managed it all the way through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's warmer, maybe we get a bit more food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we certainly don't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So unfortunately, towards the 21st, 22nd, 23rd, something like that, of March, we both applied when they came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, all you have to do is go to the front of the block and stand there till they came.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
